Template pentru prezentările CDL
================================

What you need:
 * LaTeX and Unicode for it
 * http://latex-beamer.sf.net/
 * highlight: http://www.andre-simon.de/ (just apt-get it, it's called
highlight)
 * you also need to tell me if anything's wrong.

Intrucţiuni:
 * run `make' in top dir; should be enough, as it also makes in code/
 * dacă adăugaţi cod nou, update the makefile

